32
00:01:11,340 --> 00:01:12,870
Times have indeed changed,

33
00:01:12,870 --> 00:01:15,720
and so are the challenges
young people face today.

34
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:17,940
Yes, our generation worked hard,

35
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:20,010
but that doesn't mean
young people aren't working

36
00:01:20,010 --> 00:01:21,540
