37
00:01:21,540 --> 00:01:23,572
Jake is juggling school and a job

38
00:01:23,572 --> 00:01:25,620
and planning for his future.

39
00:01:25,620 --> 00:01:28,110
The world is honestly more complex now.

40
00:01:28,110 --> 00:01:29,700
The path to success isn't

41
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:31,860
as straightforward as it used to be.

42
00:01:31,860 --> 00:01:32,880
We need to support

43
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:36,090
