generation, not belittle them.

44
00:01:36,090 --> 00:01:39,180
They're the backbone of
future leaders of this world.

45
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,712
We should be guiding
them with our experience,

46
00:01:41,712 --> 00:01:43,740
not dismantling their efforts.

47
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:46,200
I wish I could tell you I
changed his views on youngsters,

48
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:49,110
